                  </persName>
            . I was at the corner of Charles-street. A number of children were round a shew - I saw the prisoners there; Marks put his arm on the shoulder of Kendrick's child - Lazarus went round behind. I saw the clasp of the necklace move round the child's neck, and all at once it was gone. I seized the prisoners and another. The necklace was picked up.</p>
               <p>
            
